trade_df["MA_3"] = trade_df.groupby("TIPO_DATO")["OBS_VALUE"].transform(
    lambda x: x.rolling(window=3).mean()
)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
after_2013 = trade_df["TIME_PERIOD"] >= "2013"
is_ESAV = trade_df["TIPO_DATO"] == "ESAV"
is_ISAV = trade_df["TIPO_DATO"] == "ISAV"

plt.plot(
    "TIME_PERIOD",
    "OBS_VALUE",
    data=trade_df[is_ESAV & after_2013],
    marker="",
    color="blue",
    linewidth=1,
)
plt.plot(
    "TIME_PERIOD",
    "OBS_VALUE",
    data=trade_df[is_ISAV & after_2013],
    marker="",
    color="red",
    linewidth=1,
)
plt.plot(
    "TIME_PERIOD",
    "MA_3",
    data=trade_df[is_ESAV & after_2013],
    marker="",
    color="blue",
    linewidth=0.5,
)
plt.plot(
    "TIME_PERIOD",
    "MA_3",
    data=trade_df[is_ISAV & after_2013],
    marker="",
    color="red",
    linewidth=0.5,
)

plt.axhline(y=100, color="black", linewidth=0.5, linestyle="-")
plt.legend()
plt.ylim((20000, 44000))
plt.rcParams["figure.figsize"] = (15, 4)
